Daniel M. DAVIS, petitioner,
v.
Charles C. CRAFTS, et al.
No. 17-6981.
Supreme Court of the United States
Feb. 20, 2018.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Idaho dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
